text: Szalejów Górny () is a village in the administrative district of Gmina Kłodzko, within Kłodzko County, Lower Silesian Voivodeship, in south-western Poland. Prior to 1945 it was in Germany. It lies approximately west of Kłodzko, and south-west of the regional capital Wrocław. ==References== Category:Villages in Kłodzko County
title: Szalejów Górny
